{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "pmo-ip-smoke-gate-2026",
    "name": "PMO Dashboard — Phase IP Smoke Validation Gate",
    "description": "Aggregate validation gate for the entire I-track (IG through IQ). MUST pass before any new implementation phase is authorized.\n\nGATES:\n  IP-V1: Backend restarted AFTER Phase IN commit (operator confirms)\n  IP-V2: {{op_id}} and {{staff_user_id}} set by 00-B and 00-C\n  IP-V3: All 8 folders execute without 400/404/500\n  IP-V4: 10-A pillar-summary — accomplishment_rate_pct > 0 (Phase IN)\n  IP-V5: 10-B quarterly-trend — actual_rate_q1..q4 non-null (Phase IN)\n  IP-V6: 13-A..13-D assignment CRUD (Phase IJ)\n  IP-V7: 14-A..14-C workflow DRAFT → PENDING_REVIEW → PUBLISHED\n\nEXECUTION ORDER (STRICT):\n  00-A → 00-B → 00-C\n    → 10-A → 10-B → 10-C → 10-D\n    → 11-A → 11-B → 11-C\n    → 12-A → 12-B\n    → 13-A → 13-B → 13-C → 13-D\n    → 14-A → 14-B → 14-C\n    → 15-A → 15-B\n    → 99-A\n\nPRE-CONDITIONS:\n  - Backend running at {{base_url}} after `npm run build` + restart\n  - Admin credentials valid (used by 00-A)\n  - FY 2025 has ≥ 1 operation per pillar with at least one indicator where target_q1 > 0 and accomplishment_q1 > 0 (otherwise 10-A/10-B will correctly report zeros and gate fails)\n\nSTOP ON FIRST HARD-GATE FAILURE. Consult the Decision Matrix in `docs/plan.md` Phase IP Step IP-3.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string", "description": "Backend base URL" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "JWT — auto-set by 00-A" },
    { "key": "op_id", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "HIGHER_EDUCATION FY2025 operation UUID — auto-set by 00-B" },
    { "key": "staff_user_id", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Staff user UUID — auto-set by 00-C" },
    { "key": "ij_first_assignment_id", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Auto-set by 13-B for 13-C idempotency check" },
    { "key": "qr_id", "value": "", "type": "string", "description": "Quarterly report UUID — auto-set by 14-A" },
    { "key": "fiscal_year", "value": "2025", "type": "string", "description": "Target fiscal year for analytics gates" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 — Pre-Flight",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "00-A: Login as Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access_token);",
                  "pm.test('IP-V2a: 00-A status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('IP-V2a: 00-A token populated', () => pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('token')).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Authenticate as Admin. Populates {{token}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "00-B: Seed op_id (HIGHER_EDUCATION FY 2025)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('IP-V2b: 00-B status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "const rows = Array.isArray(body) ? body : (body.data || []);",
                  "pm.test('IP-V2b: 00-B returned at least one operation', () => pm.expect(rows.length, 'FY2025 HIGHER_EDUCATION must exist').to.be.at.least(1));",
                  "if (rows.length > 0) pm.collectionVariables.set('op_id', rows[0].id);",
                  "pm.test('IP-V2b: op_id populated', () => pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('op_id')).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/university-operations?operation_type=HIGHER_EDUCATION&fiscal_year={{fiscal_year}}&limit=1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "university-operations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "operation_type", "value": "HIGHER_EDUCATION" },
                { "key": "fiscal_year", "value": "{{fiscal_year}}" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "1" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Auto-sets {{op_id}} from first HIGHER_EDUCATION operation in FY {{fiscal_year}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "00-C: Seed staff_user_id",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('IP-V2c: 00-C status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "const rows = Array.isArray(body) ? body : (body.data || []);",
                  "const staff = rows.find(u => Array.isArray(u.roles) ? u.roles.includes('Staff') : u.role === 'Staff');",
                  "pm.test('IP-V2c: Staff user found', () => pm.expect(staff, 'at least one Staff user must exist').to.exist);",
                  "if (staff) pm.collectionVariables.set('staff_user_id', staff.id);",
                  "pm.test('IP-V2c: staff_user_id populated', () => pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('staff_user_id')).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users"]
            },
            "description": "Auto-sets {{staff_user_id}} from first user with Staff role."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
